This paper deals with automatic machine learning systems and bias, which falls under the category of natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of datasets and statistical analysis, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses issues related to fairness and ethics, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
